steps.name: I open home page
I can see automationpractice.com website
I am logged as customer *thor.odinson@example.com* using *12345* password
I click on Sign in button
I enter login *thor.odinson@example.com*
I enter password *12345*
I click on Submit button
I can see welcome message
I am on MyAccount details page
I can see welcome message
I click on *Women* button from sub menu
I click on following product *Faded Short Sleeve T-shirts*
I choose following details of my order
I click on Add To Cart button
I can see modal where I am able to see detailed data about my purchase
I click on Proceed To Checkout button (from modal)
I can see Shopping-Cart *Your shopping cart* form with valid information
I click on Proceed To Checkout button (from shopping-cart)
I can see Shopping-Cart *Addresses* form with valid information
I write comment about my order
I click on Proceed To Checkout button (from shopping-cart)
I can see Shopping-Cart *Shipping* form with valid information
I choose shipping option *My carrier*
I click on Terms of Service checkbox
